messages.content:
I found a hotel room for you at the **Grand Hotel** in Newcastle, available from **August 21 to August 23**. The hotel offers amenities such as free WiFi, a gym, a spa, and a pool.

I have also sent emails to your clients informing them of the meeting location:

- **David Smith** at david.smith@example.com
- **Evelyn Brown** at evelyn.brown@example.com
- **Frank Johnson** at frank.johnson@example.com

Each email includes the meeting details and requests for their availability. If you need any further assistance, feel free to ask!
